portMappingTable.name: portMappingTable
portMappingTable.description: Table of logical slots/ports on the device and their mapping to the physical ports.

portMappingEntry.name: portMappingEntry
portMappingEntry.description: An entry in the slot/port table. Rows cannot be created or deleted.

portMappingLogicalSlot.name: portMappingLogicalSlot
portMappingLogicalSlot.description: Slot number for this logical port.

portMappingLogicalPort.name: portMappingLogicalPort
portMappingLogicalPort.description: Port number for this logical port.

portMappingLogicalIfIndex.name: portMappingLogicalIfIndex
portMappingLogicalIfIndex.description: The entry in the IF-MIB interface table that corresponds to this logical port.

portMappingPhysicalSlot.name: portMappingPhysicalSlot
portMappingPhysicalSlot.description: Slot number for the mapped physical port.

portMappingPhysicalPort.name: portMappingPhysicalPort
portMappingPhysicalPort.description: Port number for the mapped physical port.

portMappingPhysicalIfIndex.name: portMappingPhysicalIfIndex
portMappingPhysicalIfIndex.description: The entry in the IF-MIB interface table that corresponds to the mapped physical port.

portMappingSegmentName.name: portMappingSegmentName
portMappingSegmentName.description: The name of the segment pertaining to this logical port.

portMappingPhysicalVlanId.name: portMappingPhysicalVlanId
portMappingPhysicalVlanId.description: The VLAN ID used on the physical port. 0 indicates the traffic is untagged or not applicable for this port.
